Text:
You're being too modest by saying 'simply watchable' 

This is a good recording, very enjoyable!

Thanks!

Having already commented, I must update.Watched it again tonight I must say it's a great recording! I have loads of AC bootleg vids that are hard to watch and this 'aint one of them. Seems technology has come a long way. The video is good and the sound is excellent!

Don't treat this as a normal audience recording, it's so much more. If you don't love this film then you aren't a rocker. Simple as!
